Description: Provides infrastructure for defining, storing, updating, and
retrieving metadata and relationships for financial instruments. Supports
currencies, stocks, funds, bonds, futures, options, spreads, exchange
rates, and synthetic instruments, together with contract specifications,
identifiers, expiration dates, and underlying-instrument relationships.
